episodes.title: Ep 6 - Amanda Pulley Part 1 - Sex Trafficking Survivor
episodes.description:
Amanda's story of survival of a religious cult and being sold for sex by both her "boyfriend" AND her father is simultaneously gut wrenching and deeply inspiring.  Join us as we dive into Amanda's story of overcoming and becoming "Unbroken." 

James got pretty sick during the recording of this video and was mostly non-participatory.  The melphalan chemo for the transplant kicked in hard and he visibly changed during the process of this interview.  

Join us on this journey and share your experiences; let's grow and heal together.
